{
  "stem": "27507.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he put me in another drawer and kept me there for another hour or so.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally, it must have taken not so long time, but it was all-- and finally he let me out of this drawer.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somehow I think that the blockade must have partly been over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It probably was over some time already, maybe not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he put me-- and he put me next to the-- sitting on the table next to the window.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was on the ground floor, and I saw in front of me the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he brought me his ausweis, his identity card, to ask me if I thought that that was a good ausweis, you know, as if I would know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he saw if I thought that the Germans would honor it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, everybody was-- didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was only-- nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he was asking for reassurance from me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But anyway, I was sitting there, and suddenly I saw in the attic window upstairs on the other side, my cousins.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were looking for me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I jumped like a madman out of there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I jumped out of the apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I ran opposite, and they saw me as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they shouted for me, and we ran up, and I ran up and I met them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they were hiding in the attic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were-- I don't know how we got to that attic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I have some vague memory of going up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was a hall to the attic somehow, a trapdoor, and we went on in somebody's apartment on this-- up the stair-- up the ladder, and then we went through the trapdoor and up into the attic.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were up in this attic.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
